{"tid":124153,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"ONKYO E700BT 用後感","createTime":"2017-02-17T11:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T06:44:48.000Z","uid":52934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcd7dbb07a7c02df428ec0667761bf071acde7eb","tid":124153,"uid":52934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:18:09.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜入手，第一次用藍芽耳機，用左兩日想簡單講一講自己嘅用後感，用緊嘅巴打都可以一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n音質唔敢特別點評論感覺上自己有少少木耳，以前自己一直用緊215，e700bt bass我認為冇咁勁<br />\nConnection問題就有啲嚴重唔知係咪我個隻零舍柒，iphone睇VLC有好少delay，咁都可接受嘅，但係完全聽唔到telegram/whatsapp voice msg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講電話都有試過，一次正常通話，另一次頭十秒聽唔到對方講咩，要熄咗藍芽直接攞住電話講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過駁落部mbp度，睇YouTube直頭一至兩秒delay，把鬼火攞翻條215出嚟用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟手打咗上去安橋customer service，佢哋話都有其他iphone用家反映過 voice message問題，仲同我講暫時冇解決辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己本身主要用途都係用嚟去做gym，帶住黎做運動就冇乜問題嘅，後面電池都唔會整到唔舒服<br />\n帶返頭盔先，之前真係未試過用其他藍芽耳機，如果呢啲問題係正常咁就真係冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7339fa7e08e1bf0638837b8e63fcf9575613a94","tid":124153,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:22:18.000Z","msg":"唔做資料搜集就買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72b82f757e2b217c0919e0f0d4769fa8acdc2c6","tid":124153,"uid":52934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔做資料搜集就買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係女朋友送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔識哩方面野，純粹見我提過下想要wireless就揀左哩隻俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e0bea8a97f2c991de3abd8c52b73da54b448af","tid":124153,"uid":19789,"like":0,"dislike